    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Modular Inverses With the Extended Euclidean Algorithm]]></title>
    <link href="http://romanprzygodzki.github.io/blog/2014/11/01/modular-inverses-with-the-extended-euclidean-algorithm/"/>
